[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":271},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2022\u002F01\u002F01\u002Freceive-google-adsense-wire-transfer-payouts-richart-taiwan\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2022\u002F01\u002F01\u002Freceive-google-adsense-wire-transfer-payouts-richart-taiwan\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2022\u002F01\u002F01\u002Freceive-google-adsense-wire-transfer-payouts-richart-taiwan\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2022\u002F01\u002F01\u002Freceive-google-adsense-wire-transfer-payouts-richart-taiwan\u002F":246,"related:\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2022\u002F01\u002F01\u002Freceive-google-adsense-wire-transfer-payouts-richart-taiwan\u002F":255},"\u002Fother\u002F20220101\u002F2179285582\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":225,"date":226,"description":227,"extension":228,"lang":229,"meta":230,"navigation":231,"path":232,"readingMinutes":233,"seo":234,"standalone":235,"stem":236,"tags":237,"tldr":243,"updated":243,"url":244,"__hash__":245},"content\u002Fen\u002FMisc\u002Freceive-google-adsense-wire-transfer-payouts-richart-taiwan.md","Receiving Google AdSense Wire-Transfer Payouts (Richart \u002F Taiwan Example)","9285582172",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":217},"minimark",[11,16,20,30,34,37,40,47,50,56,59,81,87,90,96,99,114,120,123,128,134,137,143,146,152,156,163,169,172,178,181,187,193,196,202,205,209],[12,13,15],"h2",{"id":14},"intro","Intro",[17,18,19],"p",{},"My AdSense balance finally hit the payout threshold, so I'm writing down how I set up wire transfer using Richart (Taishin International Bank, Taiwan).",[21,22,23],"blockquote",{},[17,24,25,29],{},[26,27,28],"strong",{},"Note","\nThis walkthrough uses Richart as the example, since that's what I use in Taiwan. The AdSense-side fields and process are universal across countries — only the bank specifics differ. The minimum payout threshold for wire transfer is $100 USD globally.",[12,31,33],{"id":32},"adsense-payout-setup","AdSense payout setup",[17,35,36],{},"Once your blog hits the payout minimum (~$100 USD), you can claim. Walking through wire transfer via Richart.",[17,38,39],{},"Open Google AdSense → Payments → \"Add payment method\":",[17,41,42],{},[43,44],"img",{"alt":45,"src":46},"Add payment method","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96_2021-12-30_17_00_06.png",[17,48,49],{},"Pick \"Add wire transfer details\":",[17,51,52],{},[43,53],{"alt":54,"src":55},"Add wire transfer details","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-01-01%2000.45.11.png",[17,57,58],{},"The form needs:",[60,61,62,66,69,72,75,78],"ul",{},[63,64,65],"li",{},"Beneficiary ID",[63,67,68],{},"Bank account name",[63,70,71],{},"Bank name",[63,73,74],{},"SWIFT BIC",[63,76,77],{},"Account number",[63,79,80],{},"Confirm account number",[17,82,83],{},[43,84],{"alt":85,"src":86},"Wire fields","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-01-01%2000.51.11.png",[17,88,89],{},"For Richart users — open the Richart mobile app → Foreign Exchange → \"See more\":",[17,91,92],{},[43,93],{"alt":94,"src":95},"Foreign exchange","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F202201010053.png",[17,97,98],{},"You'll see your foreign-currency account details:",[60,100,101,104,106,108,111],{},[63,102,103],{},"English account name",[63,105,77],{},[63,107,71],{},[63,109,110],{},"Branch",[63,112,113],{},"International wire code (SWIFT\u002FBIC)",[17,115,116],{},[43,117],{"alt":118,"src":119},"Account details","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F202201010057.png",[17,121,122],{},"Note these down and head back to the AdSense wire form. Fill it in:",[17,124,125],{},[26,126,127],{},"PS — Bank account name = your English name. The screenshot shows the bank name as placeholder for demo purposes.",[17,129,130],{},[43,131],{"alt":132,"src":133},"Filled form","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F202201010059.png",[17,135,136],{},"Save. Once your balance hits the $100 threshold, AdSense automatically wires the payout to that account:",[17,138,139],{},[43,140],{"alt":141,"src":142},"Auto payout","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F202201010101.png",[17,144,145],{},"You'll get a notification each payout cycle:",[17,147,148],{},[43,149],{"alt":150,"src":151},"Payout notice","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F202201010102.png",[12,153,155],{"id":154},"after-the-wire-arrives-richart-specific","After the wire arrives (Richart-specific)",[17,157,158,159,162],{},"About 5 days later, the wire arrives in Richart. Heads up — Richart requires you to manually ",[26,160,161],{},"claim"," the incoming wire. Open Richart → Foreign Exchange and you'll see a \"pending receipt\" status:",[17,164,165],{},[43,166],{"alt":167,"src":168},"Pending receipt","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F202201182030.png",[17,170,171],{},"Tap in to see the Google payout:",[17,173,174],{},[43,175],{"alt":176,"src":177},"Google payout","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F202201182037.png",[17,179,180],{},"Scroll down → pick the transaction purpose → confirm:",[17,182,183],{},[43,184],{"alt":185,"src":186},"Receive","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F202201082039.png",[17,188,189],{},[43,190],{"alt":191,"src":192},"Received","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F202201182042.png",[17,194,195],{},"Now the funds show up in your USD foreign-exchange account:",[17,197,198],{},[43,199],{"alt":200,"src":201},"USD account","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F202201182043.png",[17,203,204],{},"That's the actual money in hand.",[12,206,208],{"id":207},"heads-up","Heads up",[60,210,211,214],{},[63,212,213],{},"Use a foreign-currency account (USD-capable). AdSense pays in USD.",[63,215,216],{},"Claim incoming wires within 5 days. After that, Richart auto-returns the wire to AdSense.",{"title":218,"searchDepth":219,"depth":219,"links":220},"",2,[221,222,223,224],{"id":14,"depth":219,"text":15},{"id":32,"depth":219,"text":33},{"id":154,"depth":219,"text":155},{"id":207,"depth":219,"text":208},"Misc","2022-01-01 01:02:02","Five-minute walkthrough of setting up Google AdSense wire-transfer payouts. The bank used here is Richart (Taishin International Bank, Taiwan) — the specifics are Taiwan-flavored, but the general flow (find your foreign-currency account details, fill in AdSense's wire details form, wait for the $100 threshold, claim the incoming wire) applies to AdSense payouts in any country.","md","en",{},true,"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002Freceive-google-adsense-wire-transfer-payouts-richart-taiwan","2",{"title":6,"description":227},false,"en\u002FMisc\u002Freceive-google-adsense-wire-transfer-payouts-richart-taiwan",[238,239,240,241,242],"Richart","Taishin Bank","Google AdSense Payout","Google AdSense","Wire Transfer",null,"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2022\u002F01\u002F01\u002Freceive-google-adsense-wire-transfer-payouts-richart-taiwan\u002F","y1u8yF-w3tP3-zArjzCd3G2-IMQu-GMbJbFIpLJJgbo",{"newer":247,"older":251},{"url":248,"title":249,"date":250},"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2022\u002F01\u002F04\u002Fcommon-http-status-codes-2xx-4xx-5xx\u002F","Common HTTP Status Codes — 2xx, 4xx, 5xx Explained","2022-01-04 10:04:06",{"url":252,"title":253,"date":254},"\u002Fen\u002Fnuxt\u002F2021\u002F12\u002F26\u002Fnuxt-2x-handbook-06-head-config\u002F","Nuxt.js 2.x Hands-On Handbook (6) — Head Configuration","2021-12-26 16:53:22",[256,261,266],{"url":257,"title":258,"date":259,"readingMinutes":260},"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2026\u002F06\u002F23\u002Fmac-stats-menu-bar-system-monitor\u002F","Stats — The Free Open-Source macOS Menu Bar System Monitor I Use Every Day (CPU, GPU, Temperature, Network)","2026-06-23 10:00:00","5",{"url":262,"title":263,"date":264,"readingMinutes":265},"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2026\u002F05\u002F26\u002Fhow-much-does-a-blog-really-earn-with-google-adsense\u002F","Can a Blog Really Make Tens of Thousands of Dollars a Month? Real Google AdSense Numbers, Explained","2026-05-26 21:00:00","6",{"url":267,"title":268,"date":269,"readingMinutes":270},"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2026\u002F05\u002F18\u002Fvscode-disable-integrated-browser-auto-open\u002F","VSCode Opens Every Link in the Integrated Browser? How to Disable Auto Takeover","2026-05-18 14:30:00","4",1784010281661]